com.amplifyframework.predictions.tensorflow.asset

Interface Loadable<V,E extends java.lang.Exception>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the data type of the resource being loaded
    E - the error type for this resource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextClassificationDictionary, TextClassificationLabels, TextClassificationModel

    public interface Loadable<V,E extends java.lang.Exception>
    Defines the behavior of a loadable resource.

    • Method Summary

      • onLoaded

        Loadable<V,E> onLoaded(Consumer<V> onLoaded,
                       Consumer<E> onLoadError)
        Sets the consumer of the loaded value to be triggered upon load completion. Triggers the error consumer upon encountering an error while loading.
        Parameters:
        onLoaded - the consumer of the loaded value
        onLoadError - the consumer of the thrown exception
        Returns:
        this loadable instance for chaining
